Module org.tquadrat.bloodpressure
Package org.tquadrat.bloodpressure

Record Class DataNode

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
org.tquadrat.bloodpressure.DataNode
Record Components:
systolic - The systolic pressure in mmHG.
diastolic - The diastolic pressure in mmHG.
pulsePressure - This is the difference between the systolic and the diastolic pressure.
@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: DataNode.java 119 2022-02-10 18:55:45Z tquadrat $") @API(status=STABLE, since="0.0.1") public record DataNode(int systolic, int diastolic, int pulsePressure) extends Record

An instance of DataNode holds only the systolic and diastolic pressures as integer values, based on mmHG, but not the timestamp.

It is used for the inputs to the reports.
